Break out the guts of ceph_get_caps into a helper that takes an inode
and ceph_file_info instead of a file pointer.

Signed-off-by: Xiubo Li <xiubli@redhat.com>
Signed-off-by: Jeff Layton <jlayton@kernel.org>
